Some also said their Internet is
too slow

282
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,580
so they failed to book a room.

283
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:26,260
[What a pity! I didn't get it]

284
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:26,790
There are still 20 minutes left.

285
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:26,970
[Is there any spare room]

286
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,070
I'm sorry.

287
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:31,030
We still have

288
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:32,390
20 minutes left,

289
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:34,500
but our stock is already gone.

290
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,220
We can provide more rooms.

291
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:42,120
How many?

292
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,550
A hundred orders.

293
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:45,870
Add another hundred orders!

294
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:47,090
Three, two, one.

295
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,050
Link in the chat!

296
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:49,630
Add another hundred orders!

297
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,720
Three, two, one.

298
00:10:50,740 --> 00:10:51,670
Link in the chat!

299
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:55,240
Cut the crap.

300
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,380
I want another hundred rooms.

301
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,310
It's impossible, Mr. Duan Jr.

302
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:01,240
Please don't make this hard for me.

303
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,320
Parents and students

304
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,720
who haven't ordered yet,

305
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:08,250
-you need to seize the last chance.
-Get lost!

306
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:10,410
I also want to ask Ms. Xu.

307
00:11:16,070 --> 00:11:18,460
Is Purong Hotel offering all of its rooms

308
00:11:18,490 --> 00:11:19,630
for examinees?

309
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:20,940
Here,

310
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:24,630
on behalf of Purong Hotel, I promise

311
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:27,480
that during the exam period,
all our rooms will be reserved exclusively

312
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,500
for exam-takers.

313
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:32,390
Even if there are empty rooms, they
won't be used for other purposes.

314
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:33,120
Excellent!

315
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,150
What are you looking for?

316
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,050
Where are the car key?

317
00:11:58,050 --> 00:11:58,710
Where is it?

318
00:11:58,870 --> 00:11:59,390
Here.

319
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:05,110
Thank you. Okay.

320
00:12:24,330 --> 00:12:25,440
Where are you going?

321
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,500
To pick someone up.

322
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:35,200
That's wonderful. This is
probably the first hotel in the country

323
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:37,600
that exclusively serves families
with college entrance exam candidates.

324
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,740
I'm touched by your sincerity.

325
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:42,770
Since families with
college entrance exam-takers

326
00:12:42,770 --> 00:12:44,140
count on us,

327
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,720
we won't let you down

328
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:47,200
as Purong Hotel's principle is

329
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,750
to serve our guests with sincerity

330
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,240
and exchange sincerity for sincerity.

331
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:51,790
Oh my.

332
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:54,320
The students taking the exam
at Xinhua Finance and Economics School

333
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,330
are really lucky.

334
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:56,380
[Wishing everyone success
in the college entrance exam]

335
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,500
Sold out?

336
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,260
[Hope you can get good results]

337
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:57,660
Sold out!

338
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,420
That's wonderful.

339
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:02,290
Congratulations.

340
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:03,990
Thank you.

341
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,600
Dad, why don't you understand me at all?

342
00:13:08,850 --> 00:13:10,040
Have you had enough?

343
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,340
Have I had enough?

344
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:12,720
Why do you always think

345
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:13,810
I'm messing around?

346
00:13:13,810 --> 00:13:15,760
I've been to Kuanli so many times,

347
00:13:16,350 --> 00:13:17,750
but no one ever told me

348
00:13:17,770 --> 00:13:20,040
that the Venture Capital Summit
was moved to early June.

349
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:20,510
Why?

350
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,770
The reason they dare to treat me like this

351
00:13:22,770 --> 00:13:23,390
is because you

352
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:25,120
have never stood on my side.

353
00:13:25,610 --> 00:13:27,830
Bastard! You're useless,

354
00:13:27,850 --> 00:13:29,180
but you blame it on me.

355
00:13:29,510 --> 00:13:31,010
Duan Aoxiang, listen!

356
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,540
Kuanli Group is not your playground.

357
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,600
Doing business is not playing a game.

358
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,730
No one can
achieve a stunning success.

359
00:13:38,030 --> 00:13:39,900
You have a good hand.

360
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:42,600
Give it to me
if you don't know how to play.

361
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,440
I have plenty of talents.

362
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,200
Who is it?

363
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:18,580
Only an attendant
came up with me just now.

364
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,300
I let her go down first.

365
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:22,290
No one else heard it except me.

366
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:26,180
Don't worry. I won't tell anyone.

367
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:27,660
Come in.

368
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:08,410
I'll have an attendant come and clean up.

369
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,510
Thanks.

370
00:15:33,890 --> 00:15:35,610
[Li Qiaoqi]

371
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:36,030
Miyu, you were amazing.

372
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:37,290
I'm so happy for you.

373
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,300
[Yin Xiang]

374
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,860
Miyu, you were so beautiful
in the live stream.

375
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:40,930
Thank you.

376
00:15:41,050 --> 00:15:41,890
[Xu Miyu]

377
00:15:43,890 --> 00:15:45,510
[Lu Xiaoyan]

378
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:46,160
You are great, Ms. Xu.

379
00:15:47,570 --> 00:15:48,360
Thank you.

380
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:48,640
[Xu Miyu]

381
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:51,440
[Dianjiangchun Studio]

382
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:53,250
[Light up life and spread the beauty]

383
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:55,910
[Ji Feng]

384
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:01,200
Mr. Ji.

385
00:16:02,770 --> 00:16:04,260
Why are you here?

386
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:08,500
I'm here to welcome
the great contributor to Purong Hotel.

387
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:10,390
By the way,

388
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:12,890
I didn't have time
to ask for instructions.

389
00:16:12,910 --> 00:16:14,210
I just acted on my own.

390
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:15,650
You did a very good job.

391
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:27,000
Are you free later?

392
00:16:27,510 --> 00:16:28,770
I booked a restaurant.

393
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:30,910
I have something to say to you.

394
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:33,630
What is it?

395
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:35,960
Ms. Xu.

396
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,570
[ROSE GARDEN]

397
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:40,950
Ms. Xu.

398
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:43,130
I just told Hailin to keep you here.

399
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:45,150
I didn't expect you to leave so quickly.

400
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,090
Congratulations.

401
00:16:46,090 --> 00:16:47,510
You made a great contribution to Purong.

402
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:49,960
I should thank you for
cooperating with me.

403
00:16:49,980 --> 00:16:52,880
Otherwise, we wouldn't have
gotten such a good result.

404
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:54,720
Do you want to go for a drink later?

405
00:16:54,720 --> 00:16:56,250
Consider it a celebration.

406
00:16:59,210 --> 00:17:00,010
How about you?

407
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,700
As Purong's representative,

408
00:17:01,700 --> 00:17:03,100
do you want to come along?

409
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:06,329
I almost forgot. Thank you so much today.

410
00:17:06,829 --> 00:17:08,020
Thank you for your help.

411
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,640
Don't change the subject on purpose.

412
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,359
Are you coming or not?

413
00:17:10,359 --> 00:17:12,800
We can talk at the dinner table.

414
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,240
It wasn't easy to organize this.

415
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:19,000
You wouldn't reject me, would you?

416
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:19,960
Of course not.

417
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:23,079
Then, thank you, Ms. Jiang.

418
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:24,770
Right.

419
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:25,910
How about you?

420
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,680
Zhichun, we have to go.

421
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,790
Then I'll drive.

422
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:31,950
Take my car.

423
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:34,640
You can call a designated driver
to drive your car back later.

424
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,500
Let's go. I'll book a restaurant.

425
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:26,890
[Xu Miyu]

426
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:31,160
Let's leave together when this is over.

427
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:42,310
[Xu Miyu]

428
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:14,880
This way, please.

429
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:20,910
Thank you.

430
00:19:31,620 --> 00:19:32,250
Thank you.

431
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:37,790
Ladies, here are the menus.

432
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:38,600
Thank you.

433
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:45,740
Ms. Xu, do you
have any dietary restrictions?

434
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:47,070
I'm fine with anything.

435
00:19:49,290 --> 00:19:50,760
Their beef tartare is quite good.

436
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:51,800
Why don't we try it?

437
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:52,340
Sure.

438
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:55,880
What other appetizers would you like?

439
00:19:55,910 --> 00:19:57,840
I'd like to try the Farmhouse Soup.

440
00:19:57,920 --> 00:20:00,720
All right. We'll have three bowls of
Farmhouse Soup.

441
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:02,650
And a Chicken with Hangzhou Chili.

442
00:20:04,470 --> 00:20:05,090
And you?

443
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:09,000
Tomato and shredded pork noodles.

444
00:20:09,290 --> 00:20:10,630
You still dislike

445
00:20:10,830 --> 00:20:12,160
their cream spaghetti?

446
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:21,810
Ms. Xu, what else would you like to order?

447
00:20:25,410 --> 00:20:26,960
One Caesar Salad, please.

448
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:29,960
I remember there is mustard
in Caesar Salad, right?

449
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:30,470
Yes.

450
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,770
Sorry, Ms. Xu.

451
00:20:31,870 --> 00:20:33,510
Ji Feng is allergic to mustard.

452
00:20:33,510 --> 00:20:34,890
Should we change another one?

453
00:20:34,890 --> 00:20:35,950
It doesn't matter.

454
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:36,850
Let us take this.

455
00:20:36,850 --> 00:20:38,450
We'll have one Caesar Salad.

456
00:20:38,850 --> 00:20:40,250
I can eat a little bit now.

457
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:45,840
What else do you want to order?

458
00:20:46,290 --> 00:20:47,230
Enough for me.

459
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:48,270
Okay.

460
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:52,110
That's all for now.

461
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:52,440
Okay.

462
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,350
Enjoy your meal.

463
00:20:54,350 --> 00:20:55,280
Okay. Thank you.

464
00:21:01,650 --> 00:21:03,610
Cherish your free time.

465
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:06,340
Since you won the battle today,

466
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:08,400
you'll be busy in the following days.

467
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:12,100
The real preparation work
will begin the day after tomorrow.

468
00:21:12,100 --> 00:21:13,100
At that time,

469
00:21:13,130 --> 00:21:15,780
we welcome you to shoot and
collect more video materials.

470
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:16,510
Don't worry.

471
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:17,920
For this promotion,

472
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:20,160
I'll follow up on the whole process.

473
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:20,760
Thank you.

474
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,810
Would you like desserts?

475
00:21:31,810 --> 00:21:32,870
No need, thank you.

476
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:38,130
I know girls can't resist desserts.

477
00:21:38,510 --> 00:21:40,200
but their dessert tastes so-so.

478
00:21:40,200 --> 00:21:42,310
I know a place nearby that
I ordered from before.

479
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:44,270
After we buy what we want online

480
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:46,730
we can let Ji Feng pick it up.

481
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,240
Ms. Xu,

482
00:21:49,060 --> 00:21:51,260
see if there's anything you want to eat.

483
00:21:51,310 --> 00:21:52,270
[Sesame Crisp Biscuit] [Kai Kou Xiao]

484
00:21:53,130 --> 00:21:54,780
Then, thank you, Mr. Ji,

485
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:55,910
for making a trip for us.

486
00:21:55,910 --> 00:21:56,570
No problem.

487
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:03,980
I'll send you the screenshot.

488
00:22:04,030 --> 00:22:05,490
They serve food very fast.

489
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:06,350
Go ahead.

490
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:07,660
Okay.

491
00:22:26,110 --> 00:22:28,520
Ms. Jiang knows this restaurant very well.

492
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:30,140
It's not your first time here, is it?

493
00:22:30,140 --> 00:22:31,200
You saw through it.

494
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:34,930
You are very familiar with
everything here.

495
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:38,260
I've been here many times before.

496
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:39,940
Do you know

497
00:22:40,510 --> 00:22:42,440
when the first time I came here was?

498
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,960
It was when I won the best debater
for the first time

499
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:48,960
in a debate competition in college.

500
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:51,590
At that time,
Ji Feng didn't have much money.

501
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:53,620
He used his first internship salary

502
00:22:53,730 --> 00:22:55,390
to bring me here to celebrate.

503
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:59,070
Congratulations to Miss Jiang Zhichun
for winning the best debater.

504
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:00,640
And congratulations to you for

505
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,510
getting your first salary in life.

506
00:23:02,510 --> 00:23:02,970
Cheers.

507
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:08,800
I've started
getting the hang of it lately.

508
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,280
If everything goes well,

509
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:15,110
I can become a full-time employee
after a few more job rotations.

510
00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:22,560
Tastes good.

511
00:23:22,890 --> 00:23:24,950
The dishes just now
also tasted good.

512
00:23:25,030 --> 00:23:27,110
Let's come to this place often, okay?

513
00:23:29,790 --> 00:23:30,430
Sure.

514
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,000
My boyfriend, you are excellent.

515
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,710
I think you'll definitely
become a full-time employee.

516
00:23:36,710 --> 00:23:38,300
If you perform well,

517
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:41,060
you might even be promoted
straight to manager.

518
00:23:42,790 --> 00:23:44,270
I'll try my best.

519
00:23:56,720 --> 00:23:57,520
What's wrong?

520
00:23:58,880 --> 00:23:59,540
Too greasy.

521
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,640
Really? Let me taste it.

522
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,850
I think it's pretty good.

523
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,680
Then, I'll order it for you next time.

524
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,480
I dislike it.

525
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:22,350
Come on.

526
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:23,920
Drink some water.

527
00:24:28,270 --> 00:24:29,610
At that time, I thought

528
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,400
I was so lucky.

529
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:33,350
At the right time,

530
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,200
I was staying with the right person.

531
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:38,510
Even the randomly chosen restaurant

532
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,640
was so perfect.

533
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,690
Everything was just right.

534
00:24:42,960 --> 00:24:44,890
I didn't expect this restaurant to

535
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,760
have been open for over a decade.

536
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,610
Actually, later on,

537
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,480
I came here by myself a few times.

538
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:53,500
Maybe because my mood was different,

539
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:56,080
the dishes didn't taste the same
as before.

540
00:24:56,420 --> 00:24:58,750
Actually, there's no such thing as
"just right."

541
00:24:58,750 --> 00:24:59,810
All the perfection

542
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,480
was just him accommodating me.

543
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:06,590
He is great. But I didn't cherish him.

544
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,690
So I regret it very much now.

545
00:25:08,830 --> 00:25:11,030
I really want to mend our relationship.

546
00:25:11,260 --> 00:25:13,120
Do you think it's still possible?

547
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:24,880
Ms. Xu.

548
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:27,360
Do you feel disillusioned?

549
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:30,860
A blogger who has always
flaunted being an independent woman

550
00:25:30,860 --> 00:25:32,550
unexpectedly, in real life,

551
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,660
is so hesitant and conflicted

552
00:25:34,920 --> 00:25:36,770
when it comes to relationships.

553
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:37,480
No.

554
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,090
Thank you for your honesty, Ms. Jiang.

555
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,100
But I think

556
00:25:44,750 --> 00:25:46,550
the choice of your relationship is

557
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:48,030
in the hands of you two.

558
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:51,430
I don't know much about your past,

559
00:25:52,110 --> 00:25:54,170
and I won't interfere in your future.

560
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:55,930
If you have something to say,

561
00:25:57,440 --> 00:25:59,770
I think you'd better tell Mr. Ji directly.

562
00:26:11,990 --> 00:26:12,720
Here you are.

563
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:13,560
Thank you.

564
00:26:14,110 --> 00:26:14,910
Where is Miyu?

565
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:17,030
Ms. Xu said there's something
at the hotel,

566
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:18,630
so she went back to handle it.

567
00:26:19,590 --> 00:26:20,650
Did she just leave?

568
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:25,070
Ji Feng!

569
00:26:37,350 --> 00:26:37,880
Miyu!

570
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:44,370
I'll take you back.

571
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:46,500
No need. I've booked a rideshare.

572
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:47,920
The car is already here.

573
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:49,650
The pickup point is right here.

574
00:26:50,340 --> 00:26:52,580
Did she say something to you?

575
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,350
No.

576
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,110
There is something in the hotel.

577
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:57,030
I need to go back and handle it.

578
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,430
I'll leave it to you guys.

579
00:26:58,500 --> 00:27:00,850
Miyu, I have something to tell you.

580
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,290
Let's talk another day.

581
00:27:03,550 --> 00:27:04,480
I'm tired today.

582
00:27:22,980 --> 00:27:24,490
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

583
00:27:26,490 --> 00:27:28,150
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

584
00:27:30,350 --> 00:27:32,260
♪ People in the city ♪

585
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:36,020
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

586
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:35,830
Actually, I know very well that

587
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,410
things turning out like this

588
00:27:37,950 --> 00:27:39,760
♪ The palms of time ♪

589
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:39,700
isn't anyone's fault.

590
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:42,170
It's just that a relationship
among three people is too complicated.

591
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:44,800
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

592
00:27:43,110 --> 00:27:44,750
Those back-and-forth confrontations

593
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:46,440
have drained too much of my energy.

594
00:27:45,410 --> 00:27:47,750
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

595
00:27:47,510 --> 00:27:49,960
Maybe it's not that hard to
cheer up and face it.

596
00:27:49,330 --> 00:27:51,430
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

597
00:27:50,830 --> 00:27:51,750
But right now,

598
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:54,760
do I really need a relationship like this?

599
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:56,130
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

600
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:59,670
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

601
00:28:00,260 --> 00:28:03,380
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

602
00:28:04,110 --> 00:28:06,350
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

603
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:11,350
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

604
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:15,390
♪ The forgotten past ♪

605
00:28:16,370 --> 00:28:18,640
♪ There may be regrets ♪

606
00:28:20,300 --> 00:28:22,540
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

607
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:32,740
The stationery delivery is here.

608
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:44,790
Just put it here.

609
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:45,510
Over here.

610
00:28:58,720 --> 00:28:59,240
Come on.

611
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:00,790
Let's pack up the stationery sets.

612
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:01,750
Each requires three pencils,

613
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:02,920
one eraser,

614
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,110
one pencil sharpener,

615
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:05,400
two pens,

616
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,400
one notebook,

617
00:29:06,400 --> 00:29:07,550
plus a box of binder clips.

618
00:29:07,550 --> 00:29:08,640
We have to prepare 600 sets in total.

619
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,480
Let's do it.

620
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,070
Okay.

621
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:15,720
Tell me when you're done.

622
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,490
Ms. He,

623
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:31,570
the writing desks and
stationery for exam-takers

624
00:29:31,570 --> 00:29:32,900
have all been prepared.

625
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:33,400
Okay.

626
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:35,000
Ms. Xu instructed us

627
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:37,240
to remember to
test the internet speed at noon.

628
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:37,870
Okay.

629
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:47,320
[Purong Hotel]

630
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:45,240
Morning.

631
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,140
Hello, Ms. Xu.

632
00:29:48,390 --> 00:29:50,350
Everyone will have to work hard today.

633
00:29:50,350 --> 00:29:51,400
Guests will come here

634
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,860
one after another to check in shortly.

635
00:29:52,860 --> 00:29:54,200
Remember to carefully check

636
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:55,560
exam-takers' admission tickets.

637
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:56,200
In addition,

638
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:58,580
report any guests
with special needs immediately.

639
00:29:58,580 --> 00:29:59,700
We must meet the guests' needs

640
00:29:59,700 --> 00:30:00,920
as quickly as possible.

641
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:01,400
Yes.

642
00:30:07,350 --> 00:30:08,630
Welcome.

643
00:30:20,310 --> 00:30:21,920
Here are our ID cards

644
00:30:22,170 --> 00:30:23,130
and the child's admission ticket.

645
00:30:23,130 --> 00:30:24,660
Okay, please wait a moment.

646
00:30:26,860 --> 00:30:28,130
Stop looking at your phone.

647
00:30:28,130 --> 00:30:30,060
Pay the bill with your credit card.

648
00:30:33,790 --> 00:30:34,740
Here is your bill.

649
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:36,090
Please sign it.

650
00:30:40,110 --> 00:30:41,320
Why is this price?

651
00:30:41,350 --> 00:30:43,590
Didn't we agree on a half-price discount?

652
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:44,430
It is half price,

653
00:30:44,430 --> 00:30:45,880
but you booked the executive floor.

654
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:48,830
This is the price for a room
on the executive floor after the discount.

655
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:50,000
You booked the executive floor?

656
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,470
Our child's college entrance exam is

657
00:30:51,470 --> 00:30:52,750
the most important thing.

658
00:30:52,750 --> 00:30:54,240
Of course,
we have to stay in the best room.

659
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:56,090
This is a five-star hotel.

660
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:59,370
The accommodation and food are fine.

661
00:30:59,550 --> 00:31:01,840
Why did you book an executive suite?

662
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:05,120
Why can't we book an executive suite?

663
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:07,140
You don't usually save money.

664
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:08,640
Our kid is
taking the college entrance exam.

665
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:09,920
For such a big deal,

666
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,720
you're being stingy?

667
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,320
What kind of father are you?

668
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:15,520
I just don't think it's necessary.

669
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:17,980
Why isn't it necessary?

670
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:20,610
You snore so loudly at night.

671
00:31:20,630 --> 00:31:21,960
If I don't get a suite,

672
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,640
what if our child can't sleep well?

673
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,900
Then, you shouldn't have let my dad come.

674
00:31:25,910 --> 00:31:27,740
Liu Yuze, just be quiet.

675
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:29,240
Sorry to interrupt.

676
00:31:29,310 --> 00:31:30,410
How about this?

677
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,830
Please follow me to the executive floor

678
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:32,950
to check in.

679
00:31:32,980 --> 00:31:34,240
Come, this way please.

680
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:36,740
Hurry up.

681
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:39,110
Hurry up and go to your room
so you can start studying.

682
00:31:39,110 --> 00:31:40,310
I got you such a nice room,

683
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:41,640
but you're ungrateful.

684
00:31:43,240 --> 00:31:44,380
Welcome.

685
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,440
This way, please.

686
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:48,270
Ms. Xu.

687
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,440
The network signal for
the rooms on the east side

688
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,720
has already been tested.

689
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,050
Guests can check in now.

690
00:31:52,110 --> 00:31:54,260
The workers of the Engineering Department
are testing the west side.

691
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,440
It should be done soon.

692
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,920
Okay, I'll leave this to you.

693
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,920
By the way,
this student has some hearing problems.

694
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,030
Please take extra care of him.

695
00:32:00,030 --> 00:32:01,480
Don't worry, leave it to me.

696
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:02,070
Ms. Xu,

697
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,400
a guest in the lobby said

698
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:05,030
they didn't get the livestream booking

699
00:32:05,030 --> 00:32:06,790
but booked an exam-taker room
through the platform.

700
00:32:06,790 --> 00:32:08,660
They want to know whether
they can enjoy the discount.

701
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:10,390
Copy that. I'm coming down now.

702
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,510
I'll go then.

703
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:12,520
Get back to work.

704
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:20,350
The discount for exam-taker rooms
on the platform

705
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:22,770
and those booked through
Dianjiangchun's stream is the same.

706
00:32:22,770 --> 00:32:24,990
What about the stream's half-hour voucher?

707
00:32:24,990 --> 00:32:26,010
That takes off 20 yuan.

708
00:32:26,010 --> 00:32:27,420
This is an exclusive discount of
the live-streaming room.

709
00:32:27,420 --> 00:32:29,830
Purong can't provide
you with this discount.

710
00:32:29,830 --> 00:32:30,690
How about this?

711
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:31,990
After you check in,

712
00:32:32,020 --> 00:32:35,000
we'll give you a voucher for
the hotel's Chinese restaurant

713
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,030
as a token of our appreciation.

714
00:32:36,030 --> 00:32:37,240
Does it work for you?

715
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,130
Okay.

716
00:32:38,310 --> 00:32:40,030
Remember to send it to our room later.

717
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:40,550
Okay, no problem.

718
00:32:40,550 --> 00:32:41,590
Come on, I'll arrange it.

719
00:32:41,590 --> 00:32:42,590
This way, please.

720
00:32:49,030 --> 00:32:50,310
Give this guest

721
00:32:50,310 --> 00:32:51,240
a 30-yuan voucher.

722
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:52,240
Okay, no problem.

723
00:33:12,110 --> 00:33:13,600
Be quick.

724
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,350
Watch the heat here.

725
00:33:16,290 --> 00:33:18,100
Don't put too much oil, okay?

726
00:33:19,990 --> 00:33:21,380
How long will it take to be ready?

727
00:33:21,380 --> 00:33:22,200
Ten minutes.

728
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:23,350
Guo?

729
00:33:23,890 --> 00:33:24,520
I'm here.

730
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:26,180
Get as much of that as you have, hurry up.

731
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:26,660
Okay.

732
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:28,240
We still need two people here.

733
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:29,940
Let someone come here quickly.

734
00:33:29,940 --> 00:33:30,800
Ya?

735
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,280
-Qiaoqi.
-Ya.

736
00:33:33,330 --> 00:33:34,490
It's today's set meal.

737
00:33:34,490 --> 00:33:35,600
Where's the Yan Du Xian?

738
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:37,060
Here comes the Yan Du Xian.

739
00:33:38,510 --> 00:33:39,460
Serve it just like this.

740
00:33:39,460 --> 00:33:40,220
Okay.

741
00:33:46,310 --> 00:33:48,050
Please enjoy today's set meal.

742
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,830
Braised pork ribs. I like it.

743
00:33:51,830 --> 00:33:53,890
We'll have a cold appetizer platter,

744
00:33:54,030 --> 00:33:55,630
pork potstickers,

745
00:33:55,830 --> 00:33:58,230
scallion oil noodles and mung bean soup.

746
00:33:58,250 --> 00:33:58,910
Okay.

747
00:33:59,590 --> 00:34:00,480
Try it.

748
00:34:01,550 --> 00:34:03,220
We'd like a portion of that set meal too.

749
00:34:03,220 --> 00:34:04,680
It looks quite delicious.

750
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,480
All right.

751
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,360
Hello, distinguished guests.

752
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:12,340
Kind reminder from Purong Hotel:

753
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:13,500
it's morning now.

754
00:34:13,710 --> 00:34:15,110
The buffet restaurant opens at 6:30.

755
00:34:15,110 --> 00:34:17,110
You can come to have your breakfast.

756
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:24,170
The buffet restaurant opens at 6:30.

757
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:38,650
If the buffet restaurant is

758
00:34:38,670 --> 00:34:39,600
short of people,

759
00:34:39,639 --> 00:34:41,400
you can go help out.

760
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:43,750
I often help serve dishes.

761
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:45,070
Zhichun.

762
00:34:47,070 --> 00:34:47,760
Then, you can go back to work.

763
00:34:47,760 --> 00:34:48,360
Okay.

764
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:52,550
Why are you here?

765
00:34:52,570 --> 00:34:54,030
I'm here to shoot some footage.

766
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:55,560
Did you get what you needed?

767
00:34:55,889 --> 00:34:56,750
I got a lot.

768
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:57,510
Okay.

769
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,800
Take your time shooting.

770
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:00,740
I'll be leaving.

771
00:35:00,820 --> 00:35:02,680
Find Xue Rui if you need anything.

772
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:09,920
Let's rest for a while

773
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:12,050
and shoot when exam-takers come back.

774
00:35:14,350 --> 00:35:15,360
They are back.

775
00:35:29,330 --> 00:35:30,530
Everyone, get ready.

776
00:35:30,950 --> 00:35:31,630
Come on.

777
00:35:32,630 --> 00:35:33,360
Go. Go. Go.

778
00:36:02,370 --> 00:36:04,400
Come, serve the food.

779
00:36:04,620 --> 00:36:05,410
Come on. Here

780
00:36:10,950 --> 00:36:11,990
Come help.

781
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,120
Go.

782
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:15,460
Serve the food.

783
00:37:42,350 --> 00:37:46,360
[Xu Miyu]

784
00:38:03,550 --> 00:38:05,480
During the college entrance exam,

785
00:38:06,080 --> 00:38:08,010
Mr. Ji, you don't have other plans?

786
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,530
I'm busy.

787
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:13,060
Meiqi, two Americanos, please.

788
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:13,800
Okay.

789
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:16,780
What about you?

790
00:38:16,780 --> 00:38:18,040
What are you busy with?

791
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:20,110
I thought I'd be very busy,

792
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:22,350
but I overthought it.

793
00:38:25,710 --> 00:38:27,190
Mr. Ji, your Americanos.

794
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,620
Actually, sometimes,

795
00:38:40,190 --> 00:38:41,320
I really envy you.

796
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:44,750
The heir of Kuanli Group envies me?

797
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:50,030
Don't think
I can't tell that you're being sarcastic.

798
00:38:50,030 --> 00:38:51,480
I didn't mean that at all.

799
00:38:53,230 --> 00:38:54,360
I just think

800
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:57,240
it would be great to be like you,

801
00:38:57,260 --> 00:38:59,120
who can do whatever you want to do.

802
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,750
The feeling of fighting for
something for yourself

803
00:39:04,750 --> 00:39:06,280
must be really good, right?

804
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:09,940
What are you trying to say?

805
00:39:14,230 --> 00:39:16,110
Honestly, I don't know what I want to say.

806
00:39:16,110 --> 00:39:17,880
Ever since I was born,

807
00:39:18,030 --> 00:39:20,360
I've been doing
what my dad wanted me to do.

808
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:23,800
He asks for so much.

809
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:25,880
I can never satisfy him.

810
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:28,510
I look like a loser.

811
00:39:29,870 --> 00:39:30,400
Mr. Duan.

812
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:33,040
If you give up so early,

813
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:35,360
I'll think that in terms of
our VAM agreement,

814
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:36,420
I have already won.

815
00:39:38,770 --> 00:39:39,770
How could that be?

816
00:40:08,950 --> 00:40:11,210
Our hotel has never been so empty.

817
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:13,650
Only for now.

818
00:40:13,680 --> 00:40:14,630
At noon,

819
00:40:14,630 --> 00:40:16,880
they all rushed back to eat and sleep.

820
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:18,460
It was packed with people over there.

821
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:19,670
So scary.

822
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:22,430
Xiaoyan,

823
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:25,270
how did your cousin do
on his exam this morning?

824
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:26,920
I don't know.

825
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,480
He didn't say anything when I asked him.

826
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:30,560
He used his phone all noon,

827
00:40:30,630 --> 00:40:32,830
checking answers with his classmates.

828
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,480
Looks like they're back.

829
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,280
They are back.

830
00:40:41,370 --> 00:40:42,770
HSKP Department. HSKP Department.

831
00:40:42,770 --> 00:40:44,110
Finish the turndown service
as soon as possible.

832
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,000
The guests are back.

833
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:47,130
Ready? If so, send them out right away.

834
00:40:47,220 --> 00:40:49,140
Is tonight's supper menu ready?

835
00:40:49,710 --> 00:40:50,370
Right here.

836
00:40:51,150 --> 00:40:52,190
You can take a look,
I'll deal with something.

837
00:40:52,190 --> 00:40:52,550
Okay.

838
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,240
Ms. Xu. Ms. Xu.

839
00:40:57,280 --> 00:41:00,080
A guest at the front desk is
complaining about a lost valuable.

840
00:41:00,080 --> 00:41:01,610
Got it, I'll be right there.

841
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:06,270
My son's hearing aid was customized.

842
00:41:06,700 --> 00:41:08,470
You just said you hadn't found it.
That is it?

843
00:41:08,470 --> 00:41:09,590
What am I supposed to do?

844
00:41:09,590 --> 00:41:10,670
What about
tomorrow's English listening exam?

845
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:11,550
What is my son going to do?

846
00:41:11,550 --> 00:41:13,070
Ma'am, please calm down.

847
00:41:13,090 --> 00:41:14,670
What is the point of giving me water?

848
00:41:14,670 --> 00:41:16,780
What I want is my son's hearing aid.

849
00:41:17,110 --> 00:41:18,840
Ma'am, please calm down first.

850
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:20,600
I'll help you solve
whatever the problem is.

